From: Andi Kleen <>
Subject: [PATCH for review] [77/145] x86_64:  Calgary IOMMU: fix error path memleak in calgary_free_tar
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
